{"type": "article", "id": 44486, "title": "Tiffany 还是不景气，以及，麦当劳推出限量版汉堡盒手袋 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-08-25T03:21:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 738, "name": "麦当劳"}, {"id": 43484, "name": "BEAMS"}, {"id": 16156, "name": "Acne Studios"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 9470, "name": "Vans"}, {"id": 1864, "name": "Tiffany"}, {"id": 991, "name": "New Balance"}, {"id": 39187, "name": "菲董"}, {"id": 36613, "name": "J.W Anderson"}, {"id": 2961, "name": "Karl Lagerfeld"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 42, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170825103530FvKNlg8m4GMc3rip.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/tiffany-co-sees-modest-sales-gains-but-keep-falling-10965933/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Tiffany 发布第二季度财报，同店销售额连续七个季度下滑</strong></a> | 第二季度，Tiffany 的营收上涨了 3%，至 3.06 亿美元，净收入上涨了 9%，至 1.15 亿美元。该公司指出，亚太地区的增长推动了销售，另有分析指出，时尚珠宝品类和 Lady Gaga 这个新代言人形象，弥补了它在婚戒品类上的营收下滑。这个季度里，Tiffany 新增了三家门店，同时关闭了四家店。</p><p><a href=\"http://www.nbd.com.cn/articles/2017-08-24/1141607.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>New Balance 在华打赢商标侵权诉讼，获赔 150 万美元</strong></a> | 据《中国知识产权杂志》称，苏州市中级人民法院对新百伦公司起诉深圳市新平衡运动体育用品有限公司（New Boom）等山寨 N 字鞋生产商、销售商一案作出一审判决， New Boom 必须停止侵权及不正当竞争行为，并赔偿原告 150 万美元损失，这是在华外国企业迄今为止获得的最大一笔商标侵权赔偿金。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170825103758SPlXsueJqI2Dv7jx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>在九月柏林的 Bread &amp; Butter 展会期间，<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/08/24/karl-lagerfeld-vans-collaboration/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Karl Lagerfeld 要和 Vans 合作推出联名款</a>。据称，该系列完美地融合了两个品牌各自的风格，包括经典鞋款 Sk8-Hi、Old Skool 和 Slip-On，以及皮革背包等服饰。该系列将于 9 月 7 日正式登陆全球各大 Karl Lagerfeld 及 Vans 指定店铺，售价 40 到 300 美元不等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170825103740SRqxDKfoO9YQidtN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/458676\" rel=\"nofollow\">日本潮牌 BEAMS 旗下的女装支线 Ray BEAMS 发布了 2017 最新秋冬系列</a>。衣服倒是还不错，就是模特…很像是个杂耍艺术家。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170825103832amhspHB2GDiK8q9o.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170825104132OM3dkWtTIfo4hNqP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170825104143Zona6B5xTlJSI0sV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170825104139xvbhMtVDfQSa7WHK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708251042166dRBhgAw0m1TWLCU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170825104141WqT9oKjkAzvcEbJZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170825104142vrL7ZMDHd2qp4Xhn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170825104148X5a8vUAjH0iLBD1J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170825104155W6l3mIXnJPLquOrx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170825104158Qc15sID39H7FBbfn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170825104206ogqtUfeOWAcHrIF4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170825104221r8qVSsn21IWiCTe7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170825104212DBKby2OwECuVIY8S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170825104212ylpoXD8Jf7GYUPBA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170825104218WP2kVaXK5msUZA4E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170825104227sleM3TC94SpyqmJQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/8/uniqlo-j-w-anderson-2017-fall-winter-lookbook\" rel=\"nofollow\">优衣库和 J.W Anderson 联名款</a>将于 9 月 22 日正式发售，现已发布了官方宣传大片。来看看：<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170825104725Gl81U5qyzAJ6BxQ7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170825104627Slk0uNHgjEp5Df7C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170825104627g6ZITOlbnderKwMk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170825104626YLKjl0AVyEcehQDr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708251046289Fj7fpehXEnoGA03.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170825104628Fy9RukTUDx8zd3I6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170825104629espVlTdRSb8q1U7W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170825104823Weh8dQ0gz2o6cCsD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170825104823iGQlZbetaXkIqgM9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170825104822E02amdSpX6DY8jI5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/08/24/acne-studios-baker-bag/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Acne Studios 也跟风出了款购物袋</a>。而且还是百分百聚酰胺制作的，和普通的纸质购物袋一样，不过要卖 437 美元。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170825104707BAiDvIrtT4JExgK8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170825104707Z8uU2IT3QSWn1hdy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170825104708Oljtgo49iEkHyhvB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170825104713DJPfpNvkKVuTxQHF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"https://popbee.com/beauty/perfumes/diptyque-launched-car-air-freshener/\" rel=\"nofollow\">人气香水品牌 Diptyque 将于 9 月首次推出车载香氛产品</a>。该系列将会有多种品牌的经典香气选择，比如 34、Ambre、Figuier、Roses、Fleur D’oranger 和 Gingembre，售价 60 美元，据称可以使用三个月。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170825104852QlZvhUnHFEOkWgKs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.200000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/461255\" rel=\"nofollow\">菲董 Pharrell Williams 为 adidas 设计的网球系列正式上架</a>。该系列包括男女装及帽子等配饰，据称灵感来自 70 年代的网球明星，色调非常丰富。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170825104907sV3vq8U7XAKCBm9t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170825104911OJwSDaTv7HbuFoBz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708251049120CTuwYImRaSFEJXV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170825104915hjqwdGCeXu2DPBJA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/julien-macdonald-unveils-collaboration-mcdonalds-10965890/\" rel=\"nofollow\">麦当劳邀请英国设计师 Julien Macdonald 合作</a>，为其设计了一款巴洛克风格的金色印花限量版汉堡盒手袋。这款手袋将出现在英国麦当劳店举办的一系列展示活动中。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708251049397NrKMEs5InydBUuC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.648438\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p><p class=\"\">题图来自：<a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/458676\" rel=\"nofollow\"><i>wwd</i></a></p>"}